Package: OmicsLake
Title: OmicsLake: Versioned, On-Disk Omics Data Management for Bioconductor
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "Yusuke", family = "Matsui", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "you@example.org")
Author: Yusuke Matsui
Maintainer: Yusuke Matsui <you@example.org>
Description: A lightweight framework for versioned, on-disk omics data management using DuckDB + Arrow + Parquet.
    Provides simple read/write-style functions and Bioconductor-compatible readers (SummarizedExperiment, MultiAssayExperiment).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3)
Imports: jsonlite, digest, arrow, dplyr, dbplyr, DBI, duckdb, Matrix, SummarizedExperiment, S4Vectors, R6, rlang, tools
Suggests: qs, MultiAssayExperiment, HDF5Array, DelayedArray, knitr, rmarkdown, testthat (>= 3.0.0), igraph
biocViews: Infrastructure, DataImport, DataRepresentation
